📌 1. What is Agentic RAG?

Basic RAG:

```text
Query → Retrieve → Generate → Done
```

Agentic RAG:

```text
Query
  ↓
Agent decides retrieval strategy
  ↓
Retrieve
  ↓
Evaluate context
  ↓
Refine query (if needed)
  ↓
Retrieve again
  ↓
Generate answer
```

👉 Agentic RAG adds **planning + evaluation + iteration**.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🧠 Simple Definition

> Agentic RAG = RAG system where an agent controls how and when retrieval happens.

